[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0617","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0831","title":"Linux Kernel Syslog 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux syslogd 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 syslog 服务发送大量网络连接请求，耗尽系统日志处理资源，导致 syslogd 崩溃或停止响应，无法正常记录日志。该漏洞影响多个 Linux 发行版本，攻击条件简单，无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害等级中等。建议升级版本或限制网络访问以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0831"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:08.923","remediation":"升级 sysklogd 至 1.3 及以上版本（该版本修复了并发连接处理缺陷）；若使用 Caldera OpenLinux，安装 CSSA-1999-035.0 安全补丁。现代环境建议迁移至 rsyslog 或 syslog-ng 替代传统 syslogd，并在防火墙层面限制 UDP/TCP 514 端口的来源 IP 范围，仅允许受信日志发送端访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/809"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0617.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0987","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 域认证机制存在安全缺陷，当域用户在登录时输入的域名末尾包含空格字符，系统无法正确下载并应用域安全策略，导致绕过身份认证。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，攻击者只需拥有域账户，通过在域名后附加空格即可触发。利用方式简单，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。微软已发布安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0987"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.090","remediation":"建议立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本，该补丁（KB Q237923）修复了域登录时尾部空格导致策略下载失败的问题。对于无法升级的系统，应在登录流程入口处对域名字段做 Trim 处理，去除首尾空白字符，并确保域控制器和客户端统一校验域名格式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237923","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3701042200a4e64b9e2a7f3614e9e958db6af9cd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0987","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0987.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1e5167f2-8c39-4729-bfeb-a8843e869244.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fef2105ce9bc36a63673a5e0577e307a0953c8a8/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0935","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0935.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1092","title":"tin 1.40 权限配置不当本地信息泄露漏洞","description":"tin 1.40（一个Usenet新闻阅读器）在创建用户配置文件目录 `.tin` 时使用了不安全的默认权限，导致同一系统上的其他本地用户可读取该目录下的 `.inputhistory` 文件。该文件存储了用户登录新闻服务器时输入的密码等敏感信息，攻击者只需拥有本地普通用户权限即可窃取其他用户的凭据，进而访问受保护的新闻服务器资源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1092"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.303","remediation":"升级 tin 至 1.41 或更高版本，该版本已修复 .tin 目录权限问题。若无法升级，手动执行 `chmod 700 ~/.tin` 限制目录权限，并删除或移走 ~/.tin/.inputhistory 文件（或使用 `chmod 600 ~/.tin/.inputhistory` 限制该文件仅所有者可读写），防止其他本地用户读取存储的密码信息。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94286179032648&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1092","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/SAP/fosstars-rating-core/blob/7b172f42f218f6cfad42f81bd9c9ef49de35b919/docs/oss/security/google/tink.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1092.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88535/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000883.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0935.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0935.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0935.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0528","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0793","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer JavaScript URL 重定向漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0.1 及 5.0 版本中存在 JavaScript URL 重定向漏洞。远程攻击者可构造特制恶意网页，通过 JavaScript 将浏览器窗口重定向至 `file://` 协议的本地文件系统 URL，从而绕过同源策略的跨域限制，实现跨协议脚本执行。成功利用此漏洞的攻击者能够读取目标用户计算机上的任意本地文件内容，可能导致敏感信息泄露。攻击条件简单，仅需诱使用户使用受影响版本 IE 浏览器访问恶意网页即可触发，无需任何用户交互或额外权限。微软已通过 MS99-043 安全公告提供修复补丁。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0793"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.173","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-043 提供的修补程序，或升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 及以上版本。对于无法升级的旧系统，可通过禁用 Active Scripting 和限制 Internet 区域权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-043","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19559"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0528.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0528.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0903","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1051","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 脚本的默认配置存在目录限制缺陷，仅对 /etc/ 目录进行了访问限制，未对其他目录做有效过滤。远程攻击者无需认证即可通过 reply_message_attach 参数指定任意文件路径，导致服务器上任意文件被读取，包括配置文件、源码等敏感信息。该漏洞影响使用默认配置部署 FormHandler.cgi 的 Web 服务器，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1051"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.223","remediation":"立即删除或停用 FormHandler.cgi 脚本，该脚本已不再维护且存在设计缺陷。如必须使用，编辑脚本源码，将附件的基路径硬编码为固定安全目录（如 /var/lib/formhandler/attachments/），并严格校验 reply_message_attach 参数值，拒绝包含 \"../\" 等路径回溯字符的输入。同时配置 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）限制 CGI 目录下仅允许 POST 方法访问该脚本，禁止直接通过 GET 参数读取任意路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1051","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1051.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1051.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9/GHSA-6vh4-w25v-6gh9.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88494/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1051.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0903.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0951","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1110","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 Media Player ActiveX 文件存在性信息泄露漏洞","description":"Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件在 Internet Explorer 5.0 中被调用时，当指定文件不存在会返回特定错误码，导致存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意网页，通过脚本调用该 ActiveX 对象并捕获返回的错误信息，从而探测目标系统上任意文件是否存在，威胁用户隐私安全。该漏洞仅影响安装了 Windows Media Player 的 Internet Explorer 5 用户。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1110"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.477","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 Service Pack 2 以上版本，或安装 Microsoft 安全更新 MS00-009 对应补丁。如无法升级，在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 中为 Windows Media Player ActiveX 控件 CLSID 设置兼容性标志 (Flags=0x400) 以禁用 Kill Bit，阻止其在 IE 中加载。同时建议将 IE 升级至 6.0 及以上版本以彻底消除该风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34675","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/793","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19618","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1110.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1110","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1110.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mhq8-h8mw-8cgr/GHSA-mhq8-h8mw-8cgr.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1110.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000876.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153700_153800.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0951.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0951.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0901","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1050","title":"Matt Wright FormHandler.cgi 2.0 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Matt Wright 开发的 FormHandler.cgi 2.0 脚本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 reply_message_attach 参数传入 ../ 等路径穿越序列，或直接指定模板文件名为目标文件路径，从而读取服务器上的任意敏感文件。该漏洞影响 FormHandler.cgi 2.0 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1050"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.070","remediation":"建议立即从 Web 服务器中移除或停用 `FormHandler.cgi` 脚本，改用受支持的上传组件。若无法移除，可在 Perl 脚本入口处增加路径规范化校验：使用 `File::Spec->rel2abs` 解析真实路径并检查是否越界到 Web 根目录之外；同时过滤用户输入中的 `..` 和 `/` 字符，并设置严格的模板白名单。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34600","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34939","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/798","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/799","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3550","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19620","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1050","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1050.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436/GHSA-rrx8-7p59-h436.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/F/formhandler.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/798/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1050.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000873.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0901.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0909","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0909.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0835","title":"ISC BIND named 畸形 SIG 记录拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 的域名解析服务 named 在处理畸形的 SIG 资源记录时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需任何认证即可向目标 DNS 服务器发送特制的 SIG 记录查询数据包，触发 named 进程崩溃（如断言失败或段错误），导致正常的域名解析服务中断。该漏洞影响 ISC BIND 8.2.2p1 及之前版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。建议用户升级至 BIND 8.2.2p2 或更高版本修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0835"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.437","remediation":"升级 ISC BIND 至 8.2.2-p2 或更高版本（如 9.x 系列），该版本修复了 named 处理畸形 SIG 记录时的空指针解引用问题。如无法立即升级，可在边界防火墙上限制对 DNS 服务器的外部递归查询，并启用 ACL 仅允许受信来源访问。建议部署多台冗余 DNS 服务器分摊风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0909.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0651","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0651.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0851","title":"ISC BIND NAPTR 记录处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BIND 域名解析服务在处理 NAPTR 资源记录时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向运行 BIND named 服务的 Solaris 系统发送特制的 DNS NAPTR 查询请求，导致域名解析服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成目标系统无法正常提供域名解析服务，影响网络服务的正常运行。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0851"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.407","remediation":"升级 BIND 至 8.2.2 或更高版本以修复 NAPTR 记录处理缺陷，防止恶意查询导致 named 进程崩溃退出。Solaris 7 用户应安装 Sun Security Bulletin #194 中提供的补丁；Caldera OpenLinux 用户应应用 CSSA-1999-034.1 安全更新。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙上限制对 DNS 服务器的外部递归查询来源，降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0651.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0649","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0649.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0849","title":"ISC BIND 域名服务器拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND（Berkeley Internet Name Domain）是一款广泛使用的DNS服务器软件。其named守护进程在处理特制的maxdname（最大域名长度）请求时存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器发送精心构造的域名查询数据包，触发边界条件检查异常导致named进程崩溃。该漏洞影响ISC BIND 8.2.1及之前版本，攻击者利用此漏洞可合法阻断目标DNS服务，影响网络解析功能。厂商已发布补丁，建议升级至8.2.2及以上版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0849"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.170","remediation":"立即升级 ISC BIND 至 8.2.2 及以上版本，该版本已修复 maxdname 导致的拒绝服务问题。长期建议迁移至 BIND 9.x 系列，因 BIND 8 系列已停止维护。若无法升级，可在 named.conf 中限制 recursive 查询来源 IP 范围，减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0649.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0647","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0647.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0848","title":"ISC BIND 8.2/8.2.1 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"ISC BIND 8.2 及 8.2.1 版本的域名服务进程 named 存在文件描述符管理缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送大量特制的 DNS 查询请求，消耗超过 \"fdmax\" 限制的文件描述符数量，导致 named 进程耗尽系统资源而崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 ISC BIND 8.2/8.2.1 的系统，包括 IRIX 6.5.17 和 Solaris 7.0 等平台，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0848"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:11.040","remediation":"升级到 ISC BIND 8.2.2 及以上版本，该版本修复了 fdmax 文件描述符耗尽导致的拒绝服务问题。若无法升级，可在系统层面限制 named 进程可打开的文件描述符数量（ulimit -n），并监控系统日志中异常的连接请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/194","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19615"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0647.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0618","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0618.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0833","title":"ISC BIND 8.2 NXT 记录处理缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BIND 8.2 在处理 NXT 资源记录时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可向运行 BIND 8.2 的 DNS 服务器发送特制的 NXT 记录数据包，触发缓冲区溢出，导致 DNS 服务进程崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 BIND 8.2 版本的 Solaris 及其他 Unix 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高危。建议升级至 BIND 8.2 以上的修复版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0833"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:09.190","remediation":"将 BIND 升级至 8.2.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙或 TCP Wrappers 中限制对 DNS 服务（端口 53/UDP+TCP）的访问来源，仅允许受信任的 IP 段发起查询。同时禁用递归查询（`options { recursion no; };`）以降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/788"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0618.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1520","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0985","title":"CGI City CC Whois 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"CGI City 公司开发的 CC Whois 程序中的 whois.cgi 脚本存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可在域名查询参数中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等），当脚本将用户输入传递给系统 shell 执行 whois 查询时，恶意命令被一并执行，从而导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 CC Whois 1.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0985"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:27.850","remediation":"立即停用或删除 whois.cgi 脚本，该程序已停止维护且存在命令注入漏洞。如确需 Whois 查询功能，更换为主动过滤 shell 特殊字符（如 | ; & ` $）的替代实现，或禁用 CGI 执行权限。在 Web 服务器层面限制 whois.cgi 的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0985","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20433"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1520.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0955","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0955.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1112","title":"IrfanView IrfanView32 图片文件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IrfanView32 3.0.7 及更早版本在处理 Photoshop 图片文件头时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，当文件头中\"8BPS\"图像类型后跟随超长字符串时，触发栈缓冲区溢出。攻击者可构造特制的 .psd 图片文件，诱使用户在 IrfanView32 中打开，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1112"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.740","remediation":"升级 IrfanView 至最新版本（当前最新版为 4.6x 系列，已修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞）。临时缓解措施：避免打开来源不明的 Photoshop PSD 图像文件，可在文件资源管理器中取消 .psd 文件与 IrfanView 的默认关联。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://stud4.tuwien.ac.at/~e9227474/main2.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/34066","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/781","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3549","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19610","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1112","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/781/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1112.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000869.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0955.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0953","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0953.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1111","title":"Immunix StackGuard 缓冲区溢出安全绕过漏洞","description":"StackGuard（GCC 编译器缓冲区溢出保护扩展）1.21 之前版本存在安全机制绕过漏洞。攻击者可通过非线性攻击方式直接修改指向返回地址的指针，绕过 Random Canary 和 Terminator Canary 等栈保护机制，而非通过传统缓冲区溢出覆盖返回地址条目本身。该漏洞使得基于 Canary 的栈保护失效，远程攻击者在无需触发 Canary 检测的情况下即可实施缓冲区溢出攻击，严重威胁系统安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1111"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:44.603","remediation":"立即升级 StackGuard 至 1.21 或更高版本，该版本引入了 XOR Random Canary 保护机制，将 canary 值与返回地址进行异或绑定，有效防御绕过随机 canary 和终止符 canary 的非线性指针攻击。如无法立即升级，应审查代码中是否存在通过缓冲区溢出修改指针变量后指向返回地址的攻击面，避免使用 gets() 等不安全的字符串输入函数。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=94218618329838&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/786","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3524","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1111","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1111.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd6